\qj \cbpat0 {\sa0\sb0\li0\ri0\fi0\sl288\slmult1 \f0 \fs24 \cf1 \b0 {\f0 \fs20 \cf1 \b0 This table accounts for D.C. Laws enacted by the Council of the District of Columbia since January 1, 1982, which are not codified in the District of Columbia Official Code, 2001 Edition, but which have been published in the District of Columbia Register (DCR) or the District of Columbia Municipal Regulations (DCMR).}\par }

\ql \cbpat0 {\sa0\sb0\li0\ri0\fi0\sl288\slmult1 \f0 \fs24 \cf1 \b0 \par }

\qj \cbpat0 {\sa0\sb0\li0\ri0\fi0\sl288\slmult1 \f0 \fs24 \cf1 \b0 {\f0 \fs20 \cf1 \b0 The D.C. Laws Not Codified Table includes D.C. Acts that were repealed or disapproved prior to their final approval date.}\par }

\ql \cbpat0 {\sa0\sb0\li0\ri0\fi0\sl288\slmult1 \f0 \fs24 \cf1 \b0 \par }

\qj \cbpat0 {\sa0\sb0\li0\ri0\fi0\sl288\slmult1 \f0 \fs24 \cf1 \b0 {\f0 \fs20 \cf1 \b0 The table is to be used as follows: The first column denotes the D.C. Law number or Act number where indicated; the second column sets forth the short title of the D.C. Law or Act; the third column indicates the section, where applicable, of the D.C. Law or Act; and the final column indicates, by applicable citation, where published.}\par }

